    "title": "Tree conservation and restoration priority areas",
    "description": "Tree species distribution models, climate projections, trait data and spatial proxy datasets are used to map vulnerability to habitat conversion, overexploitation, fire, overgrazing and climate change. Along with existing remote sensing products on tree cover and forest height,  provide guidance on spatial targeting on the conservation, seed sourcing, and restoration actions",
